  <title>Files Plugin</title>
  <p>
    The Files plugin allows devices to securely share files and directories
    with the SFTP protocol.
  </p>

  <list>
    <title>Features</title>
    <item>
      <p>Automatically mount remote folders</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Share local SFTP server details.</p>
    </item>
  </list>

  <div>
    <title>Requirements</title>
    <p>
      To share files and folders, a SFTP server like <cmd>sshd</cmd> must be
      running. Consult the documentation for your distribution for help setting
      up an SFTP server.
    </p>
  </div>

  <section id="preferences">
    <info>
      <link type="guide" xref="index#common-tasks"/>
